lyrics:
[Verse]
In the crimson dusk, our story unfolds
The aroma of love resonates in the sunlight
Every touch, a string of memories
This perfume plucks the flowers of romance

[Chorus]
The scent of allure, weaving dreams
Elegant, luxurious, etched beautifully in the heart
A timeless fragrance of love
Whispering to the sky, charming the stars
